{"type":"message","id":"e4007964","parentId":"7fdbbeae","timestamp":"2026-04-09T02:03:46.495Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-09 03:46:54 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 428)\nSystem: [2026-04-09 03:46:58 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-09 03:53:27 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 428)\nSystem: [2026-04-09 03:53:31 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-09 04:03:46 GMT+2] Sprint check-in:\nSystem: 1. Check if TrnsBank.md has messages — if yes, wait for Tiny to lock bank before analysing\nSystem: 2. If TrnsBank ≥ 200 messages, analyse immediately (don't wait for lock)\nSystem: 3. Update memory/2026-03-25.md with current project status\nSystem: 4. Commit to git\n\nA scheduled reminder has been triggered. The reminder content is:\n\nWhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 428)\nWhatsApp gateway connected.\nWhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 428)\nWhatsApp gateway connected.\nSprint check-in:\n1. Check if TrnsBank.md has messages — if yes, wait for Tiny to lock bank before analysing\n2. If TrnsBank ≥ 200 messages, analyse immediately (don't wait for lock)\n3. Update memory/2026-03-25.md with current project status\n4. Commit to git\n\nPlease relay this reminder to the user in a helpful and friendly way.\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 9th, 2026 — 4:03 AM (Africa/Johannesburg) / 2026-04-09 02:03 UTC\n\n[Bootstrap truncation warning]\nSome workspace bootstrap files were truncated before injection.\nTreat Project Context as partial and read the relevant files directly if details seem missing.\n- MEMORY.md: 49314 raw -> 18110 injected (~63% removed; max/file).\n- If unintentional, raise agents.defaults.bootstrapMaxChars and/or agents.defaults.bootstrapTotalMaxChars."}],"timestamp":1775700226487}}
