{"type":"message","id":"69f28cc6","parentId":"3c2b26f0","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:38:00.692Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You're right. That was my outbound message to you via WhatsApp — the scheduled progress report. Not you messaging me.\n\nSo the full picture: no human input since WHO AM I session ended Apr 8. The 12:44 UTC sign-off is correct. My brief was accurate on the facts, I just misidentified my own outbound message as incoming contact from you.\n\nStill ready for Post 3 when you are."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":61036,"output":345,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61381,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775734680688}}
