{"type":"message","id":"78a5089c","parentId":"b1bc5001","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:47:17.381Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-09 13:47 GMT+2] We need to be fair here. I think there is a strong chance that some travel nurses re-visit the same unit more than once. Further, I really cannot assume that these nurses have no say in where they are going. Lastly, who said anything abot \"pre-visiting units\"?"}],"timestamp":1775735237367}}
{"type":"message","id":"9124e18c","parentId":"78a5089c","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:47:30.597Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_0b340f18-8cca-4ec9-bdbc-9a436c499bbb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat >> /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/TrnsBank.md << 'EOF'\n\n## [2026-04-09 13:47 UTC] You:\nWe need to be fair here. I think there is a strong chance that some travel nurses re-visit the same unit more than once. Further, I really cannot assume that these nurses have no say in where they are going. Lastly, who said anything about \"pre-visiting units\"?\n\n## [2026-04-09 13:47 UTC] Me:\nNotes saved. Three valid corrections:\n1. \"Most\" travel nurses is too strong — re-visits happen\n2. Nurses have agency — can't assume zero say in placement\n3. \"Pre-visiting units\" / territory mapping — not confirmed Nava practice, needs verification before claiming\n\nEditing draft now.\nEOF"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":64964,"output":341,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65305,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775735250594}}
