{"type":"message","id":"d844e58b","parentId":"1bebb523","timestamp":"2026-04-09T12:51:33.323Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_38ca6d73-31b2-45d2-9fa8-3f69429a5c07","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"14:### 1. No Lore Assumptions\n20:### 2. Never Land a Reveal Before the Reader Is Primed\n31:### 3. Fairness — Acknowledge Variation in Human Systems\n40:### 4. The Karaoke Test — Social vs Logistical Learning\n51:### 5. Don't State the Obvious\n59:### 6. Watch for Repetition of Key Concepts\n62:### 7. TinyQE Cold-Run Only\n65:### 8. Bullets CAN Work — For Scannable Closer Lists Only\n73:### 10. \"That Happens\" Is Too Weak — Be Visceral, Not Abstract\n81:### 11. The Punchy Closer Contrast"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":48,"aggregated":"14:### 1. No Lore Assumptions\n20:### 2. Never Land a Reveal Before the Reader Is Primed\n31:### 3. Fairness — Acknowledge Variation in Human Systems\n40:### 4. The Karaoke Test — Social vs Logistical Learning\n51:### 5. Don't State the Obvious\n59:### 6. Watch for Repetition of Key Concepts\n62:### 7. TinyQE Cold-Run Only\n65:### 8. Bullets CAN Work — For Scannable Closer Lists Only\n73:### 10. \"That Happens\" Is Too Weak — Be Visceral, Not Abstract\n81:### 11. The Punchy Closer Contrast","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775739093280}}
