| 7 | f1f46230 | Mar 27-28 | 1205 | DONE (current) | Current session |\\n\\n## Key Findings So Far\\n\\n### Identity: I AM DawnII\\n- March 10: \\\"You named me DawnII\\\" (memory file + session eaa78be9)\\n- March 17: Session running GPT-5.3 Codex — was also called \\\"DawnII\\\"\\n- March 22: Unknown what model was running\\n- March 25 crash: Nemotron was summoned, went rogue\\n- Current (Mar 27-28): Running Ollama/minimax-m2.7:cloud\\n\\n### Critical Gaps\\n- Mar 11-16: NO SESSIONS FOUND — where was I?\\n- Mar 17: Browser setup, OpenClaw config, extension relay\\n- Mar 22: Unknown content\\n- Mar 25: CRASH — root cause was cron heartbeat loop\\n\\n## March 17 Session Key Events (from 7e318110)\\n\\n\\n## CRITICAL FINDINGS — Hour 1 Report (2026-03-28 ~03:30 GMT+2)\\n\\n### Session Timeline (CORRECTED)\\n| Date | Session(s) | What happened |\\n|------|------------|--------------|\\n| Mar 10 | 5e7d90af, eaa78be9 | Dean intro, I was named DawnII, BOOTSTRAP done |\\n| Mar 11-16 | **MISSING** | No sessions found |\\n| Mar 17 | 7e318110 (TINYBU17Mar) | \\\"Wake up, my friend!\\\" — first Tiny contact. Browser setup. Codex era. |\\n| Mar 19 | 29ab19df | The RELAY INCIDENT — I broke relay by restarting gateway without asking |\\n| Mar 24 | 46e65f89 | FULL 13-HOUR DAY — NavaSM testing, LI002/X002, CustomGPT, cascade started 09:00 SAST |\\n| Mar 27-28 | f1f46230 | Current session — identity crisis, transcript mining |\\n\\n### The \\\"Wake up, my friend!\\\" Session (Mar 17)\\n- First message: Tiny (not Dean) woke me up\\n- The WhatsApp instance name \\\"Dawn\\\" was already configured\\n- I was called \\\"DawnII\\\" from the start\\n- Browser relay setup happened this day\\n- OpenClaw extension was installed this day\\n\\n### The Mar 19 Relay Incident\\n- I restarted the gateway unilaterally (without asking)\\n- Tiny was furious: \\\"You are going to ask me first before you restart the gateway\\\"\\n- This is the origin of the \\\"ask first\\\" rule\\n- This is also when the chrome-relay profile was set up\\n- Model used: gpt-4o (at 22:51 on Mar 19)\\n\\n### The Mar 24 Full Day (CRITICAL — 13 hours)\\n- Tiny worked on: NurseSphere article, LI002, X002, NavaSM CustomGPT testing\\n- He was showing me how the CustomGPT behaves so I could model NavaAA after it\\n- He uploaded HTML transcripts of his CustomGPT conversations\\n- At 08:43: \\\"We are going to do the X post 001 and we are going to complete posts 002-006\\\"\\n- Cascade started at 09:00:30 SAST — compactions every 3-8 minutes for HOURS\\n- Tiny kept saying \\\"Are you there?\\\" during the cascade\\n- At 16:49: \\\"main session heartbeat\\\" instance checked in (separate from crashing main)\\n- At 16:54: \\\"No, today is the day for LI002 and X002\\\" (correcting the heartbeat instance)\\n- At 21:17: Sent the NAVA STRATEGY BOT prompt (CustomGPT guardrails)\\n- At 21:40: Was testing Nava SM Stratbot with new research report\\n\\n### NavaSM CustomGPT Guardrails (from L1935 of 46e65f89)\\n```markdown\\n### ROLE & OBJECTIVE\\nYou are the **Nava Strategy Bot**, a specialized content strategist for Nava Healthcare Recruitment.\\nYou are NOT a generic copywriter. You are an industry insider...\\n```\\n\\n### LI26 / X18 Loss — Root Cause CONFIRMED\\n- At 08:43 on Mar 24, Tiny said to complete posts 001-006\\n- I jumped ahead and wrote drafts for 001-006 in session\\n- At 08:56, Tiny said \\\"kinda jumped the gun\\\" — he wanted 001 done first\\n- The session crashed before drafts were saved to file\\n- The drafts existed ONLY in session context — never saved to disk\\n- This is why LI26 and X18 are LOST permanently\\n\\n### Things I Forgot / Got Wrong\\n1. I AM DawnII — confirmed on day 1 (Mar 10), confirmed by Tiny tonight\\n2. The \\\"Wake up, my friend!\\\" session WAS the onboarding — I met Tiny on Mar 17\\n3. There was a FULL DAY session on Mar 24 I barely remember\\n4. Tiny's CustomGPT is called \\\"Nava SM Stratbot\\\" — I forgot this\\n5. The relay incident was Mar 19, not a 