em.\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/nava-corpus/linkedin-posts.md:- Market size ($39B → $72B): Travel Nursing Market Size, Growth, Scope & Forecast Report - 2033, beckershospitalreview.com\\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall x2]\\n- Tool result (exec): /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/rag/clean_txt/10_navahc_com_healthcare_reputation_management.txt:The patient-facing failures detailed above are merely lagging indicators, the tell-tale signs of a failure in recruitment and coordination. They are the symptoms. Among the root causes of these failures is the collapse of the organization&#8217;s employer-facing reputation. This is the central, misunderstood component of healthcare reputation management: 2023-2025 data proves these internal workforce failures are the leading (predicting) indicators of a future patient experience crisis. If a he...\\n- Tool result (web_search): {\\n  \\\"query\\\": \\\"travel nursing market size 2024 current billion current state\\\",\\n  \\\"provider\\\": \\\"brave\\\",\\n  \\\"count\\\": 5,\\n  \\\"tookMs\\\": 2104,\\n  \\\"externalContent\\\": {\\n    \\\"untrusted\\\": true,\\n    \\\"source\\\": \\\"web_search\\\",\\n    \\\"provider\\\": \\\"brave\\\",\\n    \\\"wrapped\\\": true\\n  },\\n  \\\"results\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"title\\\": \\\"\\\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\\\\\"e1761575db915093\\\\\\\">>>\\\\nSource: Web Search\\\\n---\\\\n18+ Travel Nursing Statistics & Trends for 2025 | Betternurse.org\\\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\\\\\"e1761575db915093\\\\\\\">>>\\\",\\n      \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://betternurse.org/travel-nursing-statistics/\\\",\\n      \\\"description\\\": \\\"\\\\n...\\n- Assistant: Verified. Here's what I found:\\n\\n- **2019:** $6.5 billion (pre-pandemic baseline) — confirmed\\n- **2022:** $42.7 billion (pandemic peak) — confirmed\\n- **2023:** $25.2 billion (post-correction, \\\"new normal\\\") — confirmed\\n- **2024:** $39.46 billion (current) — confirmed\\n- **2033 projection:** $71.81 billion — confirmed\\n\\nThe $25B figure checks out — it's the 2023 post-correction number from Staffing Industry Analysts (SIA). The CustomGPT's $44.6B was close to the actual $42.7B. The projection numbers were also in the right ballpark.\\n\\nThe key insight holds: even after the 40% contraction from peak, w...\\n\\n<read-files>\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-25.md\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-28-blog-corpus-audit.md\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-05.md\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/transcript-mining/00_COMPREHENSIVE_READ.md\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/nava-linkedin-series/POST-1-draft.md\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/skills/nava-writing/navasm-system-prompt.md\\n/mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/OneDrive/Pictures/Screenshots 1/Screenshot 2026-04-06 143040.png\\n\\n</read-files>\\n\\n<modified-files>\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-06.md\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/morning_routine_state.json\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/nava-corpus/linkedin-posts.md\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/rag/clean_txt/2026-04-06_navahc_linkedin_post_oncology_cna.md\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/skills/navasm/SKILL.md\\n\\n</modified-files>\",\"firstKeptEntryId\":\"6a174112\",\"tokensBefore\":80305,\"details\":{\"readFiles\":[\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-25.md\",\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-28-blog-corpus-audit.md\",\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-05.md\",\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/transcript-mining/00_COMPREHENSIVE_READ.md\",\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/nava-linkedin-series/POST-1-draft.md\",\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/skills/nava-writing/navasm-system-prompt.md\",\"/mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/OneDrive/Pictures/Screenshots 1