gent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\\n\\n[Subagent Task]: Draft an X (Twitter) version of Post 3 — the continuity/merry-go-round post.\\n\\n**Post 3 core:**\\nA nurse reaches week seven — knows the culture, the karaoke spots. Week thirteen, they're gone. The 13-week exit isn't random. Familiarity breeds discomfort for agencies — a nurse who knows your unit is harder to place. So the system moves them before they feel at home. Units absorb handoff errors, orientation costs, institutional knowledge that never accumulates. Nava's answer: truth at placement, follow-up after arrival, relationships that outlast the contract. \\\"Because we don't deal in 13-week merry-go-rounds.\\\"\\n\\n**Task:**\\n1. Consider: single tweet vs 2-tweet thread\\n2. The karaoke detail is the best concrete hook — use it\\n3. Bold works in X for emphasis\\n4. Aim for the minimum number of tweets needed to tell the full story\\n5. End with \\\"merry-go-rounds\\\" as the contrast word\\n6. Max 280 chars per tweet\\n\\n**Output:** Draft version(s) — 1-tweet and/or 2-tweet options. No preamble.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1775741125324,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"a5ef28f2\",\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"**Option 1 (single tweet — 280 chars):**\\n> By week seven, a nurse knows your unit's rhythm — the shorthand, the good coffee, the karaoke spot after shift. Week thirteen: they're gone. The 13-week exit isn't random. A nurse who knows your unit is harder to place. **We don't do 13-week merry-go-rounds.**\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Option 2 (2-tweet thread — karaoke hook):**\\n\\n**Tweet 1:**\\n> Week 7: knows the culture, the charge nurse's shorthand, the karaoke spot after shift. Week 13: they're gone. The 13-week exit isn't a bug — it's a feature.\\n\\n**Tweet 2:**\\n> Agencies move nurses before they feel at home. Easier to place someone who doesn't know your unit yet. **Truth at placement. Follow-up after arrival. We don't do 13-week merry-go-rounds.**\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Recommendation:** Option 1 if you want one punchy hit. Option 2 if you want the revelation (\\\"feature not a bug\\\") to breathe and land harder before the Nava answer.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"api\": \"ollama\",\n          \"provider\": \"ollama\",\n          \"model\": \"minimax-m2.7:cloud\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 10980,\n            \"output\": 1184,\n            \"totalTokens\": 12164,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"timestamp\": 1775741171277,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"b96550f1\",\n            \"seq\": 2\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"count":2,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:main:main","kind":"other","channel":"whatsapp","displayName":"whatsapp:g-agent-main-main","deliveryContext":{"channel":"whatsapp","to":"+27763674298","accountId":"default"},"updatedAt":1775741655056,"sessionId":"218db6ed-81a7-41a0-bf11-57e0f13d18ab","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","contextTokens":100000,"totalTokens":28321,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1775741655036,"childSessions":["agent:main:subagent:7cb2c3ef-ac6e-4931-a5fb-96d403b7fb6f","agent:main:subagent:48842099-b68b-4168-9305-bfa9b25cef83","agent:main:subagent:bcf4fadb-2305-467b-bbf4-256380c499af","agent:main:subagent:dcf3003f-25c1-4eea-950e-863d8e5f5efd","agent:main:subagent:1fc0273f-11f0-468f-b737-e9e43fdf82a6","agent:main:subagent:22aca887-95f0-4415-9038-d7111741aa75","agent:main:subagent:0622a00a-1803-427d-9c0a-64caed342e69","agent:main:subagent:e48901c6-6da4-4a96-845c-d7805a7c5ad