{"type":"message","id":"9b37908f","parentId":"e2d2075c","timestamp":"2026-04-09T20:20:30.207Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nThat's correct. The \"Control UI\" is the OpenClaw Gateway dashboard — it's the same interface. When you go to `http://204.168.204.198:18789` you're hitting the gateway, and the Control UI *is* the gateway's web interface.\n\nThere's no separate \"Dawn chat in a browser\" page — the gateway IS the Control UI. You log in there to manage the agent, not to have conversations.\n\nIf you're looking to chat with me through a browser rather than the TUI, the options are:\n- **Local**: `openclaw dashboard` (your local machine)\n- **Dusk VPS**: Point your browser to `http://204.168.204.198:18789` — same gateway dashboard, but running on Dusk\n\nWhat were you expecting to see?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":49871,"output":378,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50249,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775766030176}}
