{"type":"message","id":"333dc37f","parentId":"bdbc1248","timestamp":"2026-04-09T20:20:54.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n[[reply_to_current]] Sorry — let me cut through the confusion.\n\nWhen you go to `http://204.168.204.198:18789` you're hitting the OpenClaw Gateway, which serves two things at the same URL:\n\n- `/` → the **webchat interface** (conversational, what you want)\n- `/dashboard` → the **Control UI** (administrative)\n\nMost likely you were redirected to `/dashboard` because that's the default landing page for an unauthenticated session on Dusk.\n\n**Try going directly to:** `http://204.168.204.198:18789/` — that should take you to the webchat where you can chat with me.\n\nIf that redirects you back to the dashboard login, the Dusk gateway might not have webchat enabled in its config. That's a config question for Dusk — it's a 5-minute fix once they identify the right setting."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":50572,"output":495,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51067,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775766054528}}
