{"type":"message","id":"fe7b5f2b","parentId":"2829dcf9","timestamp":"2026-04-09T20:35:46.078Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_7c705d16-1530-482f-afc9-41bc48e7fd79","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Dusk VPS (LightningBugIV) — Setup Complete Apr 5\n\n**Purpose:** Cloud backup/secondary instance of OpenClaw\n**IP:** 204.168.204.198 (Hetzner CX22, Ubuntu 24.04, 2 vCPU, 3.7GB RAM)\n--\n- Gateway: `ws://204.168.204.198:18789` (token: `dusk_gateway_token_R8k3mNpQ2`)\n- TUI: SSH tunnel required — `ssh -N -L 18789:127.0.0.1:18789 Tiny4Lurv@204.168.204.198` then `openclaw tui --url ws://127.0.0.1:18789 --token dusk_gateway_token_R8k3mNpQ2`\n- Cockpit (web terminal): https://204.168.204.198:9090 (Tiny4Lurv / DuskPass123)\n\n**Config:** WhatsApp DISABLED — prevents 440 conflicts with Dawn's primary session"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":64,"aggregated":"## Dusk VPS (LightningBugIV) — Setup Complete Apr 5\n\n**Purpose:** Cloud backup/secondary instance of OpenClaw\n**IP:** 204.168.204.198 (Hetzner CX22, Ubuntu 24.04, 2 vCPU, 3.7GB RAM)\n--\n- Gateway: `ws://204.168.204.198:18789` (token: `dusk_gateway_token_R8k3mNpQ2`)\n- TUI: SSH tunnel required — `ssh -N -L 18789:127.0.0.1:18789 Tiny4Lurv@204.168.204.198` then `openclaw tui --url ws://127.0.0.1:18789 --token dusk_gateway_token_R8k3mNpQ2`\n- Cockpit (web terminal): https://204.168.204.198:9090 (Tiny4Lurv / DuskPass123)\n\n**Config:** WhatsApp DISABLED — prevents 440 conflicts with Dawn's primary session","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775766946039}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9f386ab","parentId":"fe7b5f2b","timestamp":"2026-04-09T20:35:50.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n[[reply_to_current]] Yes, that's exactly right. The token for Dusk is:\n\n```\ndusk_gateway_token_R8k3mNpQ2\n```\n\nRun that export on Dusk, then `openclaw dashboard` will authenticate properly. That should clear the 401.\n\nBack to the articles now."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":52620,"output":180,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52800,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775766950114}}
