{"type":"message","id":"198ffa85","parentId":"480e28e4","timestamp":"2026-04-09T21:10:51.065Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n[[reply_to_current]] You can. If Cockpit has a terminal option, just run:\n\n```\ncat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | grep -A5 '\"gateway\"'\n```\n\nIf it doesn't have a terminal, go to Cockpit's **Files** section and navigate to `/root/.openclaw/` (or your user's `.openclaw/`). Open `openclaw.json` directly and look for the gateway section."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":64596,"output":266,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64862,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775769051058}}
