448 - If Caddy stops, run: `sudo caddy run --config /etc/caddy/Caddyfile &`\n+449 - Docs saved: `docs/dusk-https-setup.md`\n+450 - Git committed: e2d9997\n+451 \n+452 ### AntiGravity Webapp (next phase)\n+453 - Webapp will be Node.js backend on LBIV\n+454 - Backend talks to `localhost:18789` (gateway)\n+455 - Caddy proxies `/app/` route to the Node.js app port\n+456 - Three tiers: Tiny (full), Yosef (read-only), public (demo)\n+457 \n+458 ### AWAA Articles — Humanization Pass Pending\n+459 Both articles committed, Tiny's pass needed:\n+460 - `rag_abroadworks/drafts/independent_contractor_non_compete_draft1.md` — 0.651\n+461 - `rag_abroadworks/drafts/how_to_fire_contractor_draft1.md` — 0.555\n+462 - Both weak on: vocabulary precision (0.0), linguistic integrity (0.0)\n+463 - Tiny's voice pass = the fix\n+464 ","firstChangedLine":409},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775771892642}}
